><button disabled=\"\" class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-300 cursor-not-allowed\">U</button><button disabled=\"\" class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-300 cursor-not-allowed\">V</button><button disabled=\"\" class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-300 cursor-not-allowed\">W</button><button disabled=\"\" class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-300 cursor-not-allowed\">X</button><button disabled=\"\" class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-300 cursor-not-allowed\">Y</button><button disabled=\"\" class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-300 cursor-not-allowed\">Z</button></div></div><div class=\"space-y-12\"></div><div class=\"mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-lg p-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6 text-center\">Browse by Category</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><button class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-4 text-center hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\">🥗</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Nutrition</h3></button><button class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-4 text-center hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\">💪</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Fitness</h3></button><button class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-4 text-center hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\">🧘</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Mental Health</h3></button><button class=\"bg-white rounded-lg p-4 text-center hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\">😴</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Sleep</h3></button></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Wellness Tools</h2><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"flex items-center text-neutral-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/tools#bmi\"><div class=\"bg-primary/10 p-2 rounded-full mr-3\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z\"></path></svg></div><span>BMI Calculator</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center text-neutral-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/tools#calorie\"><div class=\"bg-primary/10 p-2 rounded-full mr-3\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg></div><span>Calorie Calculator</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center text-neutral-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/tools#water\"><div class=\"bg-primary/10 p-2 rounded-full mr-3\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z\"></path></svg></div><span>Water Intake Calculator</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-center text-neutral-700 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/tools#sleep\"><div class=\"bg-primary/10 p-2 rounded-full mr-3\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z\"></path></svg></div><span>Sleep Calculator</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Healthy Living Tips</h2><ul class=\"space-y-4\"><li class=\"flex\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-primary font-bold text-lg mr-3\">01.</div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Stay Physically Active</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-600\">Aim for at least 150 minutes of moderate activity weekly.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-primary font-bold text-lg mr-3\">02.</div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Eat a Balanced Diet</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-600\">Focus on fruits, vegetables, whole grains, and lean proteins.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-primary font-bold text-lg mr-3\">03.</div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Get Enough Sleep</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-600\">Adults should aim for 7-9 hours of quality sleep each night.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-primary font-bold text-lg mr-3\">04.</div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Manage Stress</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-600\">Practice mindfulness, meditation, or relaxation techniques.</p></div></li></ul></div></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-neutral-100 pt-12 pb-6\"><div class=\"container-custom\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-4\">About HealthInfo</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/editorial-policy\">Editorial Policy</a></l